Dobro. Oprezno na stubama. čovječe.

5
00:01:05.858 --> 00:01:07.193
Dobro došli na brod.

6
00:01:07.818 --> 00:01:09.737
Napokon idemo kući.

7
00:01:10.237 --> 00:01:12.531
Imate li možda nešto sitno za jelo?

8
00:01:15.284 --> 00:01:17.378
Imate li kutiju prve pomoći?

9
00:01:17.578 --> 00:01:19.330
Ima gadan rez.

10
00:01:21.957 --> 00:01:23.459
Onda barem neko mjesto za odmor?

11
00:01:28.047 --> 00:01:29.423
Ne? Ok.

12
00:01:30.633 --> 00:01:31.634
Zdravo.

13
00:01:48.317 --> 00:01:49.693
Zero. Mi...

14
00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:55.875
Vraćamo se natrag u Costa Verde...

15
00:01:56.075 --> 00:01:57.576
...vi G.R.I.T.
- Teroristi.

16
00:02:20.307 --> 00:02:22.184
<c. s0>Na putu sam. Razumiješ?

17
00:02:25.312 --> 00:02:26.814
<c. s0>Razumiješ?

18
00:02:29.191 --> 00:02:30.242
Ovo nije dobro.

19
00:02:30.442 --> 00:02:33.571
<c. s0>Ako ne dođeš... Idi s Bogom!

20
00:02:34.321 --> 00:02:35.831
Tko bi to. do vraga. trebao doći?

21
00:02:36.031 --> 00:02:36.832
Smrt.

22
00:02:37.032 --> 00:02:39.451
S pozdravima od Romana Díaza.

23
00:02:56.844 --> 00:02:58.095
Sranje!

24
00:02:58.971 --> 00:03:00.472
Ništa ne vidim.

25
00:04:48.831 --> 00:04:49.965
To je puno krvi. B.

26
00:04:50.165 --> 00:04:53.043
Pauza. molim vas? Dajte.

27
00:05:18.485 --> 00:05:19.862
Spreman za paljbu.

28
00:05:20.654 --> 00:05:21.655
Kreni!

29
00:05:31.206 --> 00:05:33.000
Da! Odličan pogodak. B!

30
00:05:36.086 --> 00:05:37.379
Da!

31
00:05:39.465 --> 00:05:40.466
Prokleto bilo!

32
00:05:43.802 --> 00:05:44.803
B?

33
00:05:46.847 --> 00:05:49.183
Hej! Ostani sa mnom. brate.

34
00:05:49.933 --> 00:05:50.934
Hajde.

35
00:05:52.436 --> 00:05:53.437
Sranje!

36
00:05:54.730 --> 00:05:55.865
Hej.

37
00:05:56.065 --> 00:05:57.149
Izdrži.

38
00:06:22.925 --> 00:06:24.426
Ezekiel Rosenberg.

39
00:06:25.344 --> 00:06:26.762
Imate pet minuta.

40
00:06:34.853 --> 00:06:36.238
da pomognete u jednoj operaciji.

41
00:06:36.438 --> 00:06:37.523
Bilo je gubitaka.

42
00:06:39.691 --> 00:06:40.734
Puno gubitaka.

43
00:06:47.616 --> 00:06:49.168
Informacije...

44
00:06:49.368 --> 00:06:50.869
Gdje je Brandon Beckett?

45
00:06:52.454 --> 00:06:53.831
Je li još živ?

46
00:07:01.296 --> 00:07:02.297
Poteškoće?

47
00:07:03.257 --> 00:07:06.301
Vaša preciznost je... inspirativna.

48
00:07:07.219 --> 00:07:09.179
Što se. do vraga. dogodilo?

49
00:07:17.312 --> 00:07:19.148
Odveo je Brandona na sigurno.

50
00:07:23.318 --> 00:07:25.571
Dobio sam šifrirani SMS.

51
00:07:50.512 --> 00:07:51.847
Najnovije stanje:

52
00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:02.324
Tipičan sovjetski trik.

53
00:08:02.524 --> 00:08:04.535
tvrditi da su SAD

54
00:08:04.735 --> 00:08:06.361
prodrle na njihov teritorij.

55
00:08:18.415 --> 00:08:21.084
Kimnite ako ste još uvijek sa mnom.

56
00:08:28.467 --> 00:08:29.968
izbrisani s lica Zemlje.

57
00:08:31.053 --> 00:08:33.263
G.R.I.T. više ne postoji.

58
00:08:36.308 --> 00:08:38.352
Ali kvaka je u ovome. Ezekiele.

59
00:08:39.770 --> 00:08:41.021
Vaš tim je u bijegu.

60
00:08:41.647 --> 00:08:42.648
skriva se.

61
00:08:48.111 --> 00:08:50.280
Peter Stolnitz. zvani Intel Pete.

62
00:08:56.203 --> 00:08:57.871
nestao u Costa Verdeu.

63
00:08:59.373 --> 00:09:00.374
Ostali ste samo Vi.

64
00:09:09.174 --> 00:09:12.511
Zadnja šansa. Gdje je Brandon Beckett?

65
00:09:15.472 --> 00:09:16.473
Vrijeme je isteklo.

66
00:09:24.731 --> 00:09:27.192
Patriot Act? To je za teroriste.

67
00:10:03.395 --> 00:10:04.521
Zdravo. Zero.

68
00:10:07.107 --> 00:10:08.108
Gdje je moj sin?

69
00:10:14.114 --> 00:10:15.324
Sugrađani Costa Verdea.

70
00:10:21.538 --> 00:10:25.425
<c. s0>ilegalno ušao u Costa Verdeu
i ubio vladinog djelatnika

71
00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:28.754
<c. s0>kao i preko 100 vojnika.

72
00:10:37.846 --> 00:10:40.274
SAD poriče bilo kakvu umiješanost

73
00:10:40.474 --> 00:10:43.685
u incident u Costa Verdeu.

74
00:10:47.814 --> 00:10:50.275
<c. s0>ubijen od strane
američkog snajperista.

75
00:10:55.155 --> 00:10:58.292
<c. s0>Zar američki marinac
Brandon Beckett nije bio osumnjičenik?

76
00:10:58.492 --> 00:11:01.036
<c. s0>Ne. Beckett
nije ubio Bruna Díaza.

77
00:11:03.789 --> 00:11:05.757
<c. s0>Zahvaljujući njemu i njegovom
ocu Thomasu Beckettu.

78
00:11:05.957 --> 00:11:08.001
Meni to zvuči kao zataškavanje.

79
00:11:08.585 --> 00:11:12.014
<c. s0>Nije prvi put
da Costa Verde pokušava

80
00:11:12.214 --> 00:11:14.016
<c. s0>skrenuti pozornost
sa siromaštva. korupcije

81
00:11:14.216 --> 00:11:16.802
<c. s0>i brutalnosti
unutar svojih granica.

82
00:11:17.344 --> 00:11:20.355
Ovo je najnoviji pokušaj SAD-a

83
00:11:20.555 --> 00:11:24.484
<c. s0>uplitanja i kontrole
naših unutarnjih poslova.

84
00:11:24.684 --> 00:11:28.155
<c. s0>Amerikanci pomažu
tim takozvanim Phoenix pobunjenicima

85
00:11:28.355 --> 00:11:30.866
<c. s0>kako bi izazvali
nemire u Costa Verdeu.

86
00:11:31.066 --> 00:11:31.950
<i>PREMIJER ROMAN DIAZ</i>

87
00:11:32.150 --> 00:11:33.911
Ne možemo to više tolerirati!

88
00:11:34.111 --> 00:11:37.706
<c. s0>Njihovo nasilje će preko granice
doći na ulice Tierre Nuevve.

89
00:11:37.906 --> 00:11:39.166
<c. s0>Što se tiče G.R.I.T.
- a.

90
00:11:39.366 --> 00:11:42.327
<c. s0>Global Response
and Intelligence Team-a

91
00:11:45.497 --> 00:11:49.676
<c. s0>Svatko tko pripada ovoj terorističkoj
"false-flag" organizaciji.

92
00:11:49.876 --> 00:11:53.805
<c. s0>bit će progonjen i snosit će
posljedice za ovu operaciju.

93
00:11:54.005 --> 00:11:55.766
Upozoravam Ameriku.

94
00:11:55.966 --> 00:11:59.594
Platit ćete za ovu izdaju!

95
00:12:00.887 --> 00:12:02.055
<c. s0>Gracias.

96
00:12:10.981 --> 00:12:11.982
Glupo.

97
00:12:15.318 --> 00:12:16.319
Hajde. čovječe!

98
00:12:29.791 --> 00:12:32.210
Slušajte.

99
00:12:37.966 --> 00:12:40.394
<c. s0>Premijerova mornarica
nije mogla spriječiti

100
00:12:40.594 --> 00:12:42.971
<c. s0>- bijeg Becketta i G.R.I.T.
- a.

101
00:12:45.015 --> 00:12:46.057
Otac ili sin?

102
00:12:47.476 --> 00:12:49.102
Na što mislite? Brandon Beckett.

103
00:12:55.525 --> 00:12:57.235
<c. s0>sina učinio neprijateljem.

104
00:13:05.911 --> 00:13:09.164
<c. s0>Da. Vaš šef ga treba
za političke šahovske poteze.

105
00:13:17.797 --> 00:13:19.216
Tamo neće biti.

106
00:13:19.925 --> 00:13:23.678
<c. s0>Ma nemoj. Zato počinjemo
u Costa Verdeu.

107
00:13:25.931 --> 00:13:27.182
Dolazite ovamo?

108
00:13:39.277 --> 00:13:41.121
To će nam dovesti Brandona.

109
00:13:41.321 --> 00:13:42.873
<c. s0>Ubiti Becketta je zabavno.

110
00:13:43.073 --> 00:13:45.242
<c. s0>Pobrinite se da moj
novac bude spreman.

111
00:13:45.992 --> 00:13:47.085
Naravno.

112
00:13:47.285 --> 00:13:49.246
Imamo kripto račun...

113
00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:55.669
Želim pravi novac.

114
00:13:58.713 --> 00:13:59.714
Ne brinite.

115
00:14:01.925 --> 00:14:03.260
Dobit ćete svoj novac.

116
00:14:06.680 --> 00:14:07.973
Ako ne platite.

117
00:14:12.269 --> 00:14:15.188
Nazovite kad bude obavljeno.

118
00:14:27.284 --> 00:14:30.462
<c. s0>Roman je uveo medijsku blokadu
u cijelom Costa Verdeu.

119
00:14:30.662 --> 00:14:32.631
<c. s0>Nema vijesti.
nema društvenih mreža.

120
00:14:32.831 --> 00:14:35.467
<c. s0>Ali neki pobunjenici
probijaju vatrozide

121
00:14:35.667 --> 00:14:37.168
<c. s0>i šire istinu.

122
00:14:38.003 --> 00:14:40.847
<c. s0>Ima nekoliko sjajnih
memeova o Romanu Díazu.

123
00:14:41.047 --> 00:14:45.343
<c. s0>Onaj s mačkom. otvaračem za konzerve
i... to morate vidjeti.

124
00:14:59.482 --> 00:15:01.818
<c. s0>Ne djeluje kao obiteljski čovjek.

125
00:15:09.451 --> 00:15:10.827
pogubiti u vlastitoj zemlji.

126
00:15:15.248 --> 00:15:18.084
<c. s0>Skoro. Za par sati
znat ću više.

127
00:15:19.294 --> 00:15:20.962
Ako itko može. onda si to ti. Pete.

128
00:15:21.921 --> 00:15:25.342
<c. s0>Brandone. ako trebaš pomoć.
javi. Dolazimo.

129
00:15:28.553 --> 00:15:32.807
Hvala. ali... preopasno je.

130
00:15:34.351 --> 00:15:36.770
Yuki ne smije nikada ući u Costa Verde.

131
00:15:37.562 --> 00:15:40.273
Svi bi je proganjali.

132
00:16:04.506 --> 00:16:05.924
"Oluja se sprema.

133
00:16:07.884 --> 00:16:09.644
Onda uzimam svoje čizme..."

134
00:16:09.844 --> 00:16:11.805
"... i idem plesati na kiši."

135
00:16:14.474 --> 00:16:17.352
Master Guns. gospodine. Što radite ovdje?

136
00:16:17.936 --> 00:16:19.187
Došao sam vidjeti sina.

137
00:16:26.361 --> 00:16:27.370
Devon Frost.

138
00:16:27.570 --> 00:16:30.165
Bio sam izviđač vašem ocu.

139
00:16:30.365 --> 00:16:32.075
u Costa Verdeu.

140
00:16:33.618 --> 00:16:35.245
Vrlo mi je drago. gospodine.

141
00:16:35.995 --> 00:16:37.539
Taj je dobar.

142
00:16:45.130 --> 00:16:46.548
Ne idemo kući.

143
00:16:48.049 --> 00:16:50.719
Vi ste čovjek bez nacije. Beckette.

144
00:16:51.511 --> 00:16:52.512
Što?

145
00:17:00.687 --> 00:17:01.821
Ne možemo se vratiti?

146
00:17:02.021 --> 00:17:03.240
Pokušao sam.

147
00:17:03.440 --> 00:17:05.525
Nakon svega što smo učinili za domovinu.

148
00:17:06.735 --> 00:17:09.404
Brandone. pusti da se malo smiri.

149
00:17:10.613 --> 00:17:13.116
Predsjednik i Ministarstvo vanjskih poslova

150
00:17:17.787 --> 00:17:19.205
Pa to već znaš.

151
00:17:20.165 --> 00:17:21.499
Znaš kako to ide.

152
00:17:25.253 --> 00:17:26.921
Zar bih se trebao ovdje skrivati?

153
00:17:27.547 --> 00:17:29.516
Neslužbeno. možemo ostati neograničeno.

154
00:17:29.716 --> 00:17:31.685
Ostalo je samo par stražara.

155
00:17:31.885 --> 00:17:33.144
Ovdje je bilo zborno mjesto?

156
00:17:33.344 --> 00:17:35.138
Da. Trebali smo Kovalova...

157
00:17:38.725 --> 00:17:39.726
Znate što?

158
00:17:40.226 --> 00:17:41.227
Trebali biste otići.

159
00:17:47.859 --> 00:17:48.902
Neće ona.

160
00:17:53.031 --> 00:17:55.200
Osim toga. on nema saveznika...

161
00:18:00.413 --> 00:18:03.917
Onda je valjda svejedno
što se učini. zar ne?

162
00:18:06.169 --> 00:18:07.971
Što bih onda trebao učiniti?

163
00:18:08.171 --> 00:18:09.172
Borimo se.

164
00:18:09.923 --> 00:18:10.924
Borimo se.

165
00:18:11.466 --> 00:18:12.717
Kao i uvijek. B.

166
00:18:14.719 --> 00:18:16.938
Pomoći ćemo u čišćenju Costa Verdea.

167
00:18:17.138 --> 00:18:18.723
Zero. polako malo.

168
00:18:19.182 --> 00:18:20.609
Nijedna zemlja vas ne podržava.

169
00:18:20.809 --> 00:18:22.685
Sakrijte se ovdje i ostanite na sigurnom.

170
00:18:30.318 --> 00:18:31.318
Znate što?

171
00:18:31.444 --> 00:18:33.571
Pođite sa mnom u Južnu Ameriku.

172
00:18:38.368 --> 00:18:39.828
Tvoja odluka. B.

173
00:18:45.375 --> 00:18:48.044
Trebali bismo pomoći Phoenix pobuni.

174
00:18:56.135 --> 00:18:57.135
Njihova pobjeda je i naša pobjeda.

175
00:18:57.262 --> 00:18:58.680
To je puno "ako".

176
00:19:02.141 --> 00:19:03.685
Moramo razgovarati s Thabom Zondijem.

177
00:19:05.103 --> 00:19:06.604
<c. s0>Kako ste nas pronašli?

178
00:19:10.692 --> 00:19:12.819
Reci nam što se događa u Costa Verdeu.

179
00:19:16.948 --> 00:19:18.283
Na granici s Tierrom Nuevom.

180
00:19:18.992 --> 00:19:21.578
<c. s0>Poslao sam jedinicu u izviđanje.

181
00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:29.210
<c. s0>Ako ste svi ovdje.
nitko nas neće zaustaviti.

182
00:19:33.631 --> 00:19:35.341
Ne možemo se vratiti. Zondi.

183
00:19:41.306 --> 00:19:43.141
zbog međunarodnog incidenta.

184
00:19:48.354 --> 00:19:51.065
ali naći ćemo način.

185
00:20:04.829 --> 00:20:06.965
mogu dovesti zalihe na granicu.

186
00:20:07.165 --> 00:20:09.667
<c. s0>Ne trebaju nam vojni
obroci ni toaletni papir.

187
00:20:11.669 --> 00:20:13.388
<c. s0>Trebaju nam vojnici!

188
00:20:13.588 --> 00:20:16.591
<c. s0>Trebamo najboljeg
snajperista na svijetu.

189
00:20:24.891 --> 00:20:27.268
koje je na putu prema nama.

190
00:20:29.646 --> 00:20:32.482
<c. s0>Donose nam oružje
da sami vodimo ovu borbu.

191
00:20:33.441 --> 00:20:35.735
<c. s0>Ne vraćaju se da nam pomognu. Angele.

192
00:20:38.905 --> 00:20:39.906
Angel?

193
00:20:40.907 --> 00:20:42.951
<c. s0>Gospodo. razumijem vas.

194
00:20:43.701 --> 00:20:44.753
<c. s0>Ali dolaze izbori.

195
00:20:44.953 --> 00:20:46.496
<c. s0>a samo je Roman kandidat.

196
00:20:47.163 --> 00:20:48.882
<c. s0>Nitko mu se neće suprotstaviti.

197
00:20:49.082 --> 00:20:51.918
Moramo ukloniti Romanov utjecaj.

198
00:20:58.633 --> 00:21:00.635
Trebao bi biti sa svojom kćeri.

199
00:21:01.302 --> 00:21:02.720
<c. s0>Zašto si u Costa Verdeu?

200
00:21:08.059 --> 00:21:11.354
Angel. ima li još nešto?

201
00:21:12.021 --> 00:21:14.232
Sve je ovdje eskaliralo.

202
00:21:22.991 --> 00:21:26.786
<c. s0>Dakle. donosite nam oružje
na granicu. da?

203
00:21:28.663 --> 00:21:29.847
<c. s0>Onda ćemo nastaviti razgovor.

204
00:21:30.331 --> 00:21:33.292
<c. s0>Ali sat kuca. Moramo krenuti.

205
00:21:38.339 --> 00:21:41.217
<c. s0>Da. besmisleno je da se
ne borim uz vas.

206
00:21:43.344 --> 00:21:44.554
<c. s0>Uz vas sam.

207
00:21:54.689 --> 00:21:56.107
Odluka o ostanku bila je ispravna.

208
00:21:57.859 --> 00:22:00.028
Iskoristio sam ono čemu si me naučio.

209
00:22:04.073 --> 00:22:05.658
<c. s0>kod Kovalova.

210
00:22:15.293 --> 00:22:17.253
<c. s0>Želim se boriti uz tebe.

211
00:22:18.755 --> 00:22:19.756
<c. s0>Do tada.

212
00:22:20.923 --> 00:22:23.092
<c. s0>ovdje nastavljam sam.

213
00:22:26.179 --> 00:22:27.346
<c. s0>Doviđenja.

214
00:22:32.602 --> 00:22:35.113
Frost. šaljem koordinate

215
00:22:35.313 --> 00:22:36.865
za primopredaju.

216
00:22:37.065 --> 00:22:38.441
<c. s0>Spremna. Katrina.

217
00:22:40.651 --> 00:22:42.370
Zašto ovo nikada prije nismo radili?

218
00:22:42.570 --> 00:22:44.372
Zato što sam te vidio kako se boriš.

219
00:22:44.572 --> 00:22:46.165
Malo si...

220
00:22:46.365 --> 00:22:47.533
Agresivan?

221
00:22:53.331 --> 00:22:54.332
Dobro.

222
00:22:55.750 --> 00:22:56.834
Pokaži što znaš.

223
00:23:27.865 --> 00:23:28.866
Zapovjedniče Zondi.

224
00:23:30.034 --> 00:23:31.869
Pridružuju li nam se Amerikanci?

225
00:23:34.747 --> 00:23:37.133
Nije ono što sam htio. ali prihvaćamo.

226
00:23:37.333 --> 00:23:38.835
Naši vojnici su spremni.

227
00:23:41.712 --> 00:23:43.840
Trebaju nam uređaji za noćni vid.

228
00:23:48.636 --> 00:23:50.054
Ja vodim tim Alpha.

229
00:23:50.721 --> 00:23:52.440
Moramo biti spremni na sve.

230
00:23:52.640 --> 00:23:55.109
Ne želim da išta pođe po zlu.

231
00:23:55.309 --> 00:23:56.769
Pobrinut ćemo se za to...

232
00:24:00.189 --> 00:24:01.983
Pokret!

233
00:24:11.450 --> 00:24:13.911
Potrošimo malo streljiva!

234
00:25:47.672 --> 00:25:48.673
Hej.

235
00:25:51.259 --> 00:25:52.343
Jesmo li zabrljali?

236
00:25:53.261 --> 00:25:54.553
Zadnju misiju?

237
00:25:55.596 --> 00:25:56.806
Pogledaj ishod.

238
00:26:00.473 --> 00:26:01.277
Ljudi poput Stonea. Intel Petea. Yuki...

239
00:26:01.477 --> 00:26:02.987
sada su u bijegu.

240
00:26:03.187 --> 00:26:05.022
Ispunili smo misiju.

241
00:26:05.856 --> 00:26:07.984
A saznanja su donijela mnogo dobroga.

242
00:26:11.362 --> 00:26:13.364
Trenutna situacija će se riješiti.

243
00:26:14.282 --> 00:26:15.449
Uskoro ćemo moći kući.

244
00:26:18.286 --> 00:26:19.412
Ne znam.

245
00:26:24.625 --> 00:26:26.877
Ugodnije se osjećam kad imam misiju.

246
00:26:28.129 --> 00:26:31.090
Kod kuće se osjećam kao stranac.

247
00:26:32.258 --> 00:26:34.343
Ne smiješ nikoga pustiti blizu.

248
00:26:35.553 --> 00:26:37.054
jer opet moraš otići.

249
00:26:37.805 --> 00:26:39.849
Ne smiješ reći kamo ni zašto.

250
00:26:52.653 --> 00:26:54.572
Ali pojedi malo krumpir salate i za mene."

251
00:26:55.156 --> 00:26:57.616
Ali što nam je činiti?

252
00:26:58.617 --> 00:27:00.545
Kad dođe zadatak. prihvatimo ga.

253
00:27:00.745 --> 00:27:02.246
Hajde. idemo.

254
00:28:29.625 --> 00:28:30.626
Kreni!

255
00:28:52.148 --> 00:28:53.732
Vraže. To ti je bila rana.

256
00:29:00.698 --> 00:29:03.033
Daj. čovječe! Nije fora!

257
00:29:03.617 --> 00:29:05.202
Mislio sam da te stvarno boli.

258
00:29:05.870 --> 00:29:07.455
Igraš se mojim osjećajima.

259
00:29:13.335 --> 00:29:15.087
Dogodio se napad.

260
00:29:59.840 --> 00:30:01.342
<c. s0>Nadam se da ti se svidjelo. Brandone.

261
00:30:05.137 --> 00:30:06.305
<c. s0>Ti si sljedeći.

262
00:30:07.348 --> 00:30:08.474
<i>VEZA PREKINUTA</i>

263
00:30:11.227 --> 00:30:12.478
<c. s0>Most je osiguran.

264
00:30:22.196 --> 00:30:23.280
Inače bih vam

265
00:30:24.365 --> 00:30:26.492
izrezao organe jedan po jedan.

266
00:30:34.250 --> 00:30:35.251
"Koga".

267
00:30:38.128 --> 00:30:40.756
Koga. Tko će koga rasporiti.

268
00:30:48.138 --> 00:30:50.599
Broj mrtvih je 50. Za sada.

269
00:30:55.062 --> 00:30:56.438
Želite li znati zašto?

270
00:30:57.940 --> 00:30:59.275
Brandon Beckett.

271
00:31:01.652 --> 00:31:04.405
Beckett vas želi vidjeti mrtve. Sve vas.

272
00:31:09.159 --> 00:31:11.587
Kad vas je kontaktirao. ušli smo u trag

273
00:31:11.787 --> 00:31:13.956
pozivu do ovog mjesta.

274
00:31:17.084 --> 00:31:19.712
Vaš razgovor s njim bio je vaša
smrtna presuda.

275
00:31:21.755 --> 00:31:23.007
A on je to znao.

276
00:31:47.865 --> 00:31:49.658
Tome sam se i nadao.

277
00:31:51.076 --> 00:31:52.077
Legionari!

278
00:31:54.163 --> 00:31:55.164
Pokret!

279
00:32:05.424 --> 00:32:08.135
Hajde. Pođite. Pratite me.

280
00:32:08.886 --> 00:32:12.014
<c. s0>Razgovarao sam putem videopoziva
s Katrinom kad su napali.

281
00:32:12.848 --> 00:32:15.401
<c. s0>Preko 50 Phoenix pobunjenika
ubijeno je u zasjedi.

282
00:32:15.601 --> 00:32:17.236
Troje su uzeli kao taoce.

283
00:32:17.436 --> 00:32:19.572
Lorenzo. Angel i Zondi.

284
00:32:19.772 --> 00:32:20.898
Sveto sranje.

285
00:32:25.986 --> 00:32:27.196
Tko su ti tipovi?

286
00:32:29.490 --> 00:32:30.616
Željezna legija.

287
00:32:36.664 --> 00:32:38.832
Ti tipovi su "anti-G.R.I.T.".

288
00:32:42.711 --> 00:32:44.421
iz svih dijelova svijeta.

289
00:32:48.217 --> 00:32:49.927
Kilian Kruger ih vodi.

290
00:32:52.763 --> 00:32:54.607
Bivši južnoafrički specijalac.

291
00:32:54.807 --> 00:32:56.809
sada plaćeni ubojica i anarhist.

292
00:33:05.734 --> 00:33:07.861
i poslao ih brigadnom generalu.

293
00:33:18.831 --> 00:33:19.873
Francisco Cabrera

294
00:33:25.754 --> 00:33:28.090
I da pronađu vas. Brandone.

295
00:33:29.925 --> 00:33:31.260
Kako su našli skrovište?

296
00:33:35.723 --> 00:33:36.932
Preko nas.

297
00:33:46.233 --> 00:33:48.277
Legija nam ne provaljuje na vrata samo zato

298
00:33:50.612 --> 00:33:52.364
što je vatrozid probijen.

299
00:33:55.075 --> 00:33:56.660
Znači. mi smo krivi.

300
00:34:01.415 --> 00:34:03.751
Gdje Željezna legija drži taoce?

301
00:34:05.753 --> 00:34:06.754
Ne znamo.

302
00:34:15.971 --> 00:34:17.273
To je zamka.

303
00:34:17.473 --> 00:34:18.640
Nemamo izbora.

304
00:34:19.641 --> 00:34:21.944
Nećemo ostaviti Angela i Zondija
na cjedilu.

305
00:34:22.144 --> 00:34:23.145
Pronađimo ih!

306
00:34:29.318 --> 00:34:30.611
I dolaze ovamo.

307
00:34:33.155 --> 00:34:34.456
Kad se Katrina izvukla.

308
00:34:34.656 --> 00:34:36.500
mislio sam da je najsigurnije

309
00:34:36.700 --> 00:34:38.494
da ostatak napusti zemlju.

310
00:34:46.251 --> 00:34:47.251
kodnog imena "Phoenix".

311
00:34:47.419 --> 00:34:49.379
Ako itko otkrije to oružje.

312
00:34:50.756 --> 00:34:52.674
moglo bi izbrisati pobunu.

313
00:34:53.550 --> 00:34:56.053
Dakle. povlačimo se. razumijete?

314
00:35:12.236 --> 00:35:14.571
Još jednom. premijeru Díaz.

315
00:35:28.085 --> 00:35:29.845
Smatrajte ovo mjesto kreditom.

316
00:35:30.045 --> 00:35:31.839
Ako me nastavite impresionirati.

317
00:35:44.017 --> 00:35:45.018
Ali...

318
00:35:47.771 --> 00:35:49.231
Gdje je Brandon Beckett?

319
00:36:05.581 --> 00:36:06.365
Da?

320
00:36:06.415 --> 00:36:08.458
Objavite priopćenje za javnost.

321
00:36:25.976 --> 00:36:28.395
Ali... i ovo je važno...

322
00:36:29.521 --> 00:36:32.774
ostavite Brandona Becketta na životu.

323
00:36:33.692 --> 00:36:35.119
Imam planove s njim.

324
00:36:35.319 --> 00:36:36.403
Nema problema.

325
00:36:51.585 --> 00:36:53.587
Thabo Zondi.

326
00:36:54.963 --> 00:36:56.632
Znamo sve o vama.

327
00:36:58.842 --> 00:37:00.477
Niste naučili lekciju

328
00:37:00.677 --> 00:37:02.312
kad su tata i djed poginuli u borbi.

329
00:37:02.512 --> 00:37:03.772
jer ste se pridružili

330
00:37:03.972 --> 00:37:05.933
južnoafričkoj vojsci.

331
00:37:07.935 --> 00:37:11.229
Angel Anele.

332
00:37:12.064 --> 00:37:13.490
Bivša južnoafrička policajka.

333
00:37:13.690 --> 00:37:16.026
prije nego što vas je zapovjednik
Modise angažirao.

334
00:37:18.320 --> 00:37:20.038
Lorenzo.

335
00:37:20.238 --> 00:37:22.532
Niste radili s G.R.I.T.
- om.

336
00:37:23.784 --> 00:37:27.963
ali nekako ste se našli usred svega.

337
00:37:28.163 --> 00:37:30.123
Nemam ništa protiv vas u rukama.

338
00:37:31.416 --> 00:37:32.416
Nema digitalnog traga.

339
00:37:32.542 --> 00:37:35.504
Vi ste jebeni misterij.

340
00:37:38.423 --> 00:37:39.633
G.R.I.T.

341
00:37:41.134 --> 00:37:42.970
Ti seronje. a?

342
00:38:08.078 --> 00:38:09.254
Stvarno?

343
00:38:09.454 --> 00:38:10.831
Zar je to sve što imate?

344
00:38:11.540 --> 00:38:12.541
Ne. ne.

345
00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:21.258
Mogao bih vam ubiti majku.

346
00:38:23.093 --> 00:38:25.345
Ona se brine o vašoj kćeri. zar ne?

347
00:38:30.434 --> 00:38:32.144
Moraju li obje umrijeti?

348
00:38:34.646 --> 00:38:35.897
Nećete me slomiti.

349
00:38:36.982 --> 00:38:38.608
To svi kažu.

350
00:38:40.402 --> 00:38:41.737
Progovorit ćete.

351
00:39:08.930 --> 00:39:11.892
Dakle. vi ste Brandon Beckett.

352
00:39:12.350 --> 00:39:13.518
Kriv sam.

353
00:39:14.019 --> 00:39:15.270
Mnogo sam čuo o vama.

354
00:39:16.855 --> 00:39:18.574
Ja sam Zero.

355
00:39:18.774 --> 00:39:20.317
Kako ono bješe vaše ime?

356
00:39:21.151 --> 00:39:22.527
Skylar.

357
00:39:26.782 --> 00:39:28.784
Kakva je ovdje situacija s optikom?

358
00:39:30.368 --> 00:39:32.162
Je li to oružje? Phoenix?

359
00:39:33.955 --> 00:39:36.166
Ne. To je stol.

360
00:39:45.342 --> 00:39:46.510
Budi pristojna. Skylar.

361
00:39:48.011 --> 00:39:49.012
Oni su prijatelji.

362
00:39:51.056 --> 00:39:52.057
Nova?

363
00:39:52.849 --> 00:39:53.850
O. sranje.

364
00:39:56.269 --> 00:39:57.521
Živa si.

365
00:39:59.564 --> 00:40:00.565
Kako?

366
00:40:02.609 --> 00:40:03.777
Ti si oružje.

367
00:40:04.736 --> 00:40:05.737
Phoenix.

368
00:40:12.702 --> 00:40:14.788
Širim nadu. brate.

369
00:40:17.165 --> 00:40:18.165
Brate?

370
00:40:18.250 --> 00:40:19.426
Skylar je moja sestra.

371
00:40:19.626 --> 00:40:21.837
Polusestra. S majčine strane.

372
00:40:26.675 --> 00:40:29.136
Siguran sam da svi žele malo porazgovarati.

373
00:40:30.262 --> 00:40:32.606
Ali dok to radimo. pripremimo sve.

374
00:40:32.806 --> 00:40:34.766
Vrijeme nas gura. Može?

375
00:40:44.901 --> 00:40:46.444
Čovjek ima dovoljno vremena.

376
00:40:54.327 --> 00:40:56.171
Pluća vam se pune vodom.

377
00:40:56.371 --> 00:40:58.590
Nosna šupljina i grlo se zatvaraju.

378
00:40:58.790 --> 00:41:00.292
Disanje postaje otežano.

379
00:41:01.418 --> 00:41:02.419
Glava gori.

380
00:41:10.844 --> 00:41:12.771
Ako se radi pogrešno.

381
00:41:12.971 --> 00:41:14.472
smrtonosna hipoksija.

382
00:41:21.563 --> 00:41:22.856
Ako se radi ispravno.

383
00:41:23.690 --> 00:41:25.400
spora. kontrolirana smrt.

384
00:41:33.992 --> 00:41:35.744
Zadnja šansa. Zondi.

385
00:41:36.912 --> 00:41:38.338
Angel.

386
00:41:38.538 --> 00:41:39.539
Lorenzo.

387
00:41:41.458 --> 00:41:42.509
Recite mi.

388
00:41:42.709 --> 00:41:44.920
Recite mi sve o Beckettu.

389
00:41:46.463 --> 00:41:48.256
Moram proučiti Beckettov priručnik.

390
00:41:57.015 --> 00:41:58.016
U redu.

391
00:42:00.560 --> 00:42:01.561
Počnimo.

392
00:42:11.529 --> 00:42:13.240
To je dovelo do revolucije.

393
00:42:18.703 --> 00:42:19.880
Prije atentata. moj otac

394
00:42:20.080 --> 00:42:21.831
je želio trgovinu sa SAD-om.

395
00:42:22.666 --> 00:42:24.376
Nakon njegove smrti

396
00:42:28.213 --> 00:42:32.676
rekao je da naša zemlja
mora biti samoodrživa.

397
00:42:38.348 --> 00:42:39.933
Roman ne otvara granice

398
00:42:41.017 --> 00:42:42.644
zato što ih želi proširiti.

399
00:42:43.895 --> 00:42:46.982
na druge zemlje... poput Tierre Nueve.

400
00:42:49.150 --> 00:42:51.027
Ali za to mu treba rat.

401
00:42:51.611 --> 00:42:52.612
Točno.

402
00:42:54.906 --> 00:42:56.032
Sve je spremno.

403
00:42:57.867 --> 00:42:59.035
Nakon mojih ozljeda

404
00:43:00.036 --> 00:43:03.290
nisam se mogla vratiti u borbu.

405
00:43:15.593 --> 00:43:16.593
Mora ići brzo.

406
00:43:16.720 --> 00:43:18.188
Čak i sa signalnim relejem.

407
00:43:18.388 --> 00:43:20.890
mogu mu ući u trag prije ili kasnije.

408
00:43:24.144 --> 00:43:25.603
To smo naučili.

409
00:43:26.563 --> 00:43:27.689
Što možemo učiniti?

410
00:43:35.238 --> 00:43:36.323
Sranje.

411
00:43:39.909 --> 00:43:42.662
Ovo je upravo stiglo. Trenutak.

412
00:43:43.246 --> 00:43:44.840
TRI TERORISTA PRED POGUBLJENJEM!

413
00:43:45.040 --> 00:43:46.291
Dat ću da se prevede.

414
00:43:47.000 --> 00:43:48.376
TRI TERORISTA PRED POGUBLJENJEM!

415
00:43:53.256 --> 00:43:54.257
Pogubljeni?

416
00:43:57.177 --> 00:43:58.845
Roman želi dati primjer.

417
00:44:00.138 --> 00:44:01.598
Svaki takozvani "terorist".

418
00:44:10.648 --> 00:44:11.691
Kako ćemo to zaustaviti?

419
00:44:13.943 --> 00:44:14.944
Ne možemo.

420
00:44:24.287 --> 00:44:26.164
i neosvojivo je.

421
00:44:31.211 --> 00:44:32.721
a da većina ne pogine.

422
00:44:32.921 --> 00:44:34.055
Ovdje imamo pobunjenike.

423
00:44:34.255 --> 00:44:36.299
Ima nas dovoljno da jurišamo na dvorac.

424
00:44:45.975 --> 00:44:48.269
Govorimo o Angel i Zondiju!

425
00:45:18.466 --> 00:45:20.644
U redu. razumijemo. Nova.

426
00:45:20.844 --> 00:45:22.262
Poštujemo to.

427
00:45:31.146 --> 00:45:32.230
Onda sretno.

428
00:45:37.068 --> 00:45:38.236
Nova.

429
00:45:40.196 --> 00:45:41.739
Lijepo te je opet vidjeti.

430
00:45:45.869 --> 00:45:47.996
Hvala što ste nas primili.

431
00:45:50.039 --> 00:45:51.040
Ali molim te.

432
00:46:10.685 --> 00:46:12.604
Mora postojati način za ulazak.

433
00:46:16.274 --> 00:46:17.275
Ne znam.

434
00:46:53.394 --> 00:46:55.104
Ali vi to znate. zar ne?

435
00:46:56.689 --> 00:46:59.817
On je doveo Željeznu legiju ravno do vas.

436
00:47:13.581 --> 00:47:18.211
Učinit ću Costa Verde jednakom za sve.

437
00:47:31.724 --> 00:47:33.351
i vidi se kako je to završilo.

438
00:47:34.060 --> 00:47:35.812
Narod to ne želi.

439
00:47:36.980 --> 00:47:40.858
Žele zaštitu. sigurnost.

440
00:47:41.526 --> 00:47:44.070
A to je ono što ja nudim.

441
00:48:09.762 --> 00:48:14.734
Ali lojalnost Brandonu Beckettu

442
00:48:14.934 --> 00:48:17.186
ima posljedice.

443
00:49:10.323 --> 00:49:11.366
Što želite?

444
00:49:18.665 --> 00:49:20.291
Imate potencijala.

445
00:49:46.693 --> 00:49:48.444
Možete biti vođa.

446
00:50:08.464 --> 00:50:10.350
Vodite za mene.

447
00:50:10.550 --> 00:50:12.927
i učinit ću vašu ostavštinu besmrtnom.

448
00:50:37.994 --> 00:50:42.915
sve. od ovog trenutka...

449
00:50:44.917 --> 00:50:46.335
je dar od mene.

450
00:50:52.258 --> 00:50:53.760
Darujem vam život.

451
00:51:02.310 --> 00:51:03.861
Ovo je morfij.

452
00:51:04.061 --> 00:51:06.147
Ovdje sam da vam pomognem.

453
00:51:49.273 --> 00:51:51.734
U redu je. lonako sam završio.

454
00:52:08.000 --> 00:52:11.170
Sveto sranje. Pogledaj se.

455
00:52:15.424 --> 00:52:16.425
Samo želim aspirin.

456
00:52:25.476 --> 00:52:27.528
Brandon i ja ne možemo odustati.

457
00:52:27.728 --> 00:52:29.480
Izgubili smo svoj G.R.I.T. tim.

458
00:52:31.524 --> 00:52:32.984
I toliko drugih.

459
00:52:35.069 --> 00:52:36.821
Ne želim više nikoga izgubiti.

460
00:52:38.072 --> 00:52:40.741
To s G.R.I.T. timom je smiješno.

461
00:52:43.035 --> 00:52:45.037
Sve ovo vrijeme.

462
00:52:50.167 --> 00:52:53.588
da je Yuki Mifune dio vašeg tima.

463
00:53:02.513 --> 00:53:03.514
Pa.

464
00:53:05.725 --> 00:53:06.851
nitko nije savršen.

465
00:53:09.353 --> 00:53:11.447
Nova. svi smo mi obični vojnici.

466
00:53:11.647 --> 00:53:13.282
Svi smo ubijali po zapovijedi.

467
00:53:13.482 --> 00:53:15.276
Nije to ništa osobno.

468
00:53:17.153 --> 00:53:18.154
Ništa osobno?

469
00:53:26.287 --> 00:53:27.288
Da.

470
00:53:39.842 --> 00:53:40.927
Zero.

471
00:53:44.096 --> 00:53:47.483
u svakoj misiji ti si bio heroj.

472
00:53:47.683 --> 00:53:51.228
a onda bi samo nestao.

473
00:54:00.154 --> 00:54:04.292
Jer sve što činiš ima posljedice.

474
00:54:04.492 --> 00:54:08.955
Ta "Lady Death" u tvom timu. Yuki.

475
00:54:22.426 --> 00:54:24.053
Jesi li razmislio o tome?

476
00:54:34.981 --> 00:54:40.027
Već sam jednom umrla za to.

477
00:54:42.279 --> 00:54:43.698
To me promijenilo.

478
00:54:59.630 --> 00:55:00.840
Ne. čekaj. Slušaj.

479
00:55:05.261 --> 00:55:08.264
Ne mijenja! Ne!

480
00:55:38.586 --> 00:55:39.670
Laku noć. Zero.

481
00:56:06.614 --> 00:56:07.615
Zondi?

482
